===Etymology 2===
{{zh-forms|s=党}}
Identified as an ancient Chu dialect word in Han Dynasty scholar Yang Xiong's ''{{w|Fangyan}}''.

{{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}} compares it to {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*mV-taŋ||to see; to look}}, whence {{cog|bo|མཐོང||to see; to perceive}}.

Alternatively, it may be of {{cog|aav}} origin. Compare {{cog|mkh-pro|*tiɲ ~ təɲ|*tiɲ ~ *təɲ|to know}}, whence {{cog|km|ដឹង}}, {{cog|bru|ດັງ|tr=dáng}} ({{zh-ref|Behr, 2008}}; {{zh-ref|Ye, 2014}}).

Perhaps related to {{zh-l|懂|to understand}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}).

